F.29. {d}en-lil₂-me-en an-še₃ il₂-me-en ki-še₃ en me# šar₂-me-en
#lem: Enlil[1]DN; an[sky]; il[raise]; ki[place]; en[lord]; me[Being]; šar[numerous]V/i
#etcsl: line-id=F.29

